  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At the start of each of your turns during combat, you can summon one additional signature minion at no cost into an unoccupied space within your Summoner's Range (no action required).</p><p>Additionally, you can increase each of your minions' Stamina as shown on the 7th-Level Minion Stamina Increase table. Additionally, each minion that receives a Stamina boost can treat their characteristics as one higher for the purposes of resisting potencies (to a maximum value of 4).</p><p>These benefits are not reflected in the stat blocks of new minions you acquire.</p>",
      "director": ""
    },
    "source": {
      "book": "Summoner",
      "page": "40",
      "license": "Draw Steel Creator License"
    },
    "_dsid": "7th-level-minion-improvement",
